<p>

<b>Lionel Charles Jeffries</b> (born <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../805/15805.xml">
June 10</link>, <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../609/34609.xml">
1926</link> in <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../860/1202860.xml">
Forest Hill</link>, <village wordnetid="108672738" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../867/17867.xml">
London</link></village>
, <country wordnetid="108544813" confidence="0.9508927676800064">
<link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../316/9316.xml">
England</link></country>
) is a <autocracy wordnetid="108361001" confidence="0.8">
<system wordnetid="108435388" confidence="0.8">
<social_group wordnetid="107950920" confidence="0.8">
<political_orientation wordnetid="106212839" confidence="0.8">
